Privacy Policy
Effective Date: November 5, 2024

1. Data Collection and Use

Our extension collects minimal anonymous data to improve user experience and provide relevant content.

Collected data:

Demographic information: estimated gender and age group (determined based on anonymous behavioral patterns)

Usage statistics: which features of the extension are used most frequently

Technical information: browser type and OS version (to ensure compatibility)

How we use the data:

To personalize visual themes and interface

To provide more relevant content

To improve the extensionâ€™s functionality

For anonymous statistics and analytics

2. What We Do Not Collect

Personally identifiable information (name, email, phone number)

Cookies or authentication data

Browsing history or search queries

Passwords or financial information

Geolocation or precise location data

3. Data Storage and Protection

All data is stored in anonymized form and cannot be used to identify individual users.
We apply standard security measures to protect all collected data.

4. Data Sharing

We do not sell or share collected data with third parties.
Data is used solely for internal analytics and to improve the performance of the extension.

5. Consent

By using our extension, you consent to the collection and use of data in accordance with this Privacy Policy.

6. Policy Updates

We may periodically update this Privacy Policy.
Any significant changes will be communicated through extension updates.
